title: Supernatural - Complete First Season
description:
Supernatural is an American paranormal/dark fantasy/horror/thriller/drama-themed television series that debuted on September 13, 2005 on the WB Television Network, and is now part of the new CW&#039;s lineup (the show is aired on ITV in the UK, TV3 in Ireland & Network Ten in Australia). The show follows brothers Sam and Dean Winchester, who travel across the country in a black 1967 Chevy Impala investigating paranormal events and other unexplained occurrences. The show has been described by many as a cross between The X-Files and the film Frailty.

Requires Xvid or DivX. 
All 22 episodes of the first season.
Whole package is about 2,5 Gibs.
